responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "4944F4804F7B82B02B70F39E409895D7", "They were his generals who left his side, the minotaur three. First is Thunder who died in his quest to reach the clouds. Up and up he climbed, till lightning struck and his end was met. ")
